{"tid":1520162,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大搜捕是為了緊急法","createTime":"2019-08-30T17:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:21:43.000Z","uid":271176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92402b896ced02c3f9dc332d80e98898ed9f2990","tid":1520162,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:13:29.000Z","msg":"要出台緊急法有兩個重要的先決條件<br />\n<br />\n首先係確保有用 。 如果用咗緊急法，市民都唔理 ， 平息唔到示威 ，咁政府再升級就只能出解放軍。 要避免這攬炒情況，政府要確保用惡法能夠嚇到市民， 今日的大搜捕和禁止民陣遊行就是為了測試有幾多人不怕打壓<br />\n<br />\n其次係要有理據。 緊急法係大殺傷力武器， 要做，佢要有一個強力嘅藉口。 今日的大搜捕就是要令示威者更加憤怒 ，希望激發明天的衝突以製造藉口<br />\n<br />\n不知道最好的應對方法是什麼 ， 只知道投降？不了"},{"pid":"f82162ad66e469a4f1ee429da4a921c9d789c0f5","tid":1520162,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=195b242e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=705b7182\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=875b9c47\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"0a91e62158995bf52f5fcd6827035eb7ce0e0899","tid":1520162,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"咩最後一戰呀？明明就係無限之戰，你對手係赤納粹，有二三十年要捱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/15